entry.title: Jamming Mitigation Call Today
entry.summary: The message is a reminder of an upcoming jamming call scheduled on Monday, March 6 at 19:00 UTC. The link to join the call is provided as https://meet.jit.si/UnjammingLN. Additionally, participants are invited to suggest additional agenda items if any through the Github link https://github.com/ClaraShk/LNJamming/issues/5.
